text: Zigmas Gudauskas (born 25 February 1958) is a Lithuanian rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Lithuania Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
